                For the gift card’s Terms and Conditions of Use click here <a href="#">www.cominar.com/cartescadeaux-giftcard.pdf</a>
                <br />
                The Dixie Outlet Mall gift card offers great flexibility of use since it is redeemable at nearly 1,500 participating stores within Cominar’s portfolio of shopping centres. The gift card program is valid at 18 shopping centres in Quebec as well as one in Ontario.
            </p>
