            <h5 class="page_miniheads">Purchases and accepted payment methods</h5>
            <p class="page_desc">
                Cash, debit, Visa and MasterCard are accepted forms of payment. <br />
                Prepaid credit cards and personal cheques are not accepted.<br />
                Cash is accepted for purchases of $500 or less.<br />
                Photo ID is required for cash purchases of $500 or more.<br />
                Transactions exceeding $1,000 must be approved by Dixie Outlet Mall Management.<br />
                For all purchases of $3,000 or more, the card purchaser must provide the Guest Services Representative with the following information for validation: his/her first name, last name, telephone number and a piece of government issued photo ID.<br />
                Guest Services Representatives may decline any transaction they believe to be fraudulent.<br />
                Monthly maintenance fees of $2.50 will be automatically debited as of the 16th month following the gift card’s activation.<br />
            </p>
